 Ten Reasons That You Are Definitely Watching Too Much Stargate

Ten Reasons That You Are Definitely Watching Too Much Stargate.
By Aussie Mel

*From www.sg1-heliopolis.de*

1)You know the scientific definition of an Event Horizon.
2)"For Crying Out Loud" becomes part of your everyday vocabulary
T3)o you the stargate is a way of life not just a television program
4)To you a Jaffa is a warrior serving the Goa'uld and not a small red lolly
5)Your main ambition in life is to join the stargate command and travel through the stargate
6)If someone tells you the stargate is NOT real you feel the need to go into an indepth discussion on the matter explaining why the stargate IS real and the television show is just a means to cover up their tracks
7)You know the background of every character and not just the main characters
8)Your dreams regularly consist of Variations of stargate episodes
9)Science to you is studying how the stargate works
You want to go visit Colorado Springs and Chynnene Mountain 10)Despite the fact that you live on the other side of the world Eg. Australia.

If you answered yes to three or more of these then you are stargate OBSESSED.

Heee Heee Heee Join the club.

Yours truly, Aussie Mel otherwise known as Melissa Francis
